pip install pylint  --- good habits
pylint bad_code.py

Output:
************* Module bad_code
bad_code.py:1:0: C0103: Constant name "a" doesn't conform to UPPER_CASE naming style (invalid-name)
bad_code.py:2:0: C0103: Constant name "b" doesn't conform to UPPER_CASE naming style (invalid-name)
