Your code has been rated at 6.67/10


âœ… It checks code quality, not just correctness.

5. Configuration

Create a .pylintrc file in your project root:

pylint --generate-rcfile > .pylintrc


Then customize:

[MASTER]
ignore=venv,tests
[MESSAGES CONTROL]
disable=C0114,C0115,C0116  # disable docstring warnings

Now your whole team can follow the same style rules.
